      <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_patient_level_information_costing_total_cost">PATIENT LEVEL INFORMATION COSTING TOTAL COST</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_financial_amount">FINANCIAL AMOUNT</xref>
 for the purposes of 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_patient_level_information_costing">Patient Level Information Costing</xref>
    </p>
    <p>
      <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_patient_level_information_costing_total_cost">PATIENT LEVEL INFORMATION COSTING TOTAL COST</xref>
 is the total cost for each resource and 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity">ACTIVITY</xref>
 combination reported in the 
              <xref href="https://v3.datadictionary.nhs.uk/data_dictionary/messages/patient_level_information_costing_system_acute_data_set_introduction.html" scope="external" format="html">Patient Level Information Costing System Acute Data Sets</xref>.        </p>
